I can confirm that this torrent installs and registers perfectly, but I decided to uninstall it after only one use. I converted an .avi to .mkv and the video on the outputted file was jumping around like crazy. Maybe I just didn't tweak the settings properly, but I was able to convert the same .avi with the free (free!) software "Handbrake" using the default settings and had no such problem, plus the conversation took half the time.
